<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ImmoFacile CI | La Super-App du Propriétaire Ivoirien</title>
    
    <meta name="description" content="Gérez vos biens immobiliers à Abidjan : Loyers Mobile Money, Contrats numériques et Huissier en 1 clic.">
    <meta property="og:image" content="/images/immo_logo.png">
    
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/icon-512.png">
    <link rel="manifest" href="/manifest.json">
    
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0B1120">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; }
        .no-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
        .no-scrollbar { -ms-overflow-style: none; scrollbar-width: none; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 text-slate-900">

    <div class="p-4 md:p-6 lg:p-8 max-w-[1600px] mx-auto">
        
        <section class="relative rounded-[2.5rem] md:rounded-[3.5rem] overflow-hidden bg-[#0B1120] min-h-[85vh] flex flex-col shadow-2xl">
            
            <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
                <img src="/images/landing page photo.png" alt="Abidjan Plateau Skyline" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#0B1120]/90 via-[#0B1120]/60 to-transparent"></div>
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0B1120] via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
            </div>

            <nav class="relative z-20 px-8 py-8 flex justify-between items-center">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <img src="/images/immo_logo.png" alt="Logo" class="h-8 w-auto">
                    <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl tracking-tight">ImmoFacile<span class="text-[#F59E0B]">CI</span></span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8 text-sm font-medium text-gray-300">
                    <a href="#fonctionnalites" class="hover:text-white transition">Fonctionnalités</a>
                    <a href="#demo" class="hover:text-white transition">Mode d'emploi</a>
                    <a href="/login" class="hover:text-white transition">Se connecter</a>
                </div>

                <a href="/signup" class="bg-[#F59E0B] hover:bg-[#d97706] text-[#0B1120] px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold text-sm transition shadow-lg hover:scale-105">
                    S'inscrire
                </a>
            </nav>

            <div class="relative z-10 flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 pb-32 max-w-4xl">
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-[5.5rem] font-black text-white leading-[1.1] mb-8 tracking-tight">
                    Finis les impayés et <br>
                    les litiges de <br>
                    <span class="text-[#F59E0B]">caution</span> à Abidjan.
                </h1>

                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 mb-10 max-w-xl leading-relaxed font-medium">
                    La première plateforme qui automatise la collecte de vos loyers via <span class="text-white font-bold">Mobile Money</span> et sécurise vos baux avec une assistance juridique intégrée.
                </p>

                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-6">
                    <a href="/signup" class="bg-[#F59E0B] hover:bg-[#d97706] text-[#0B1120] px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg transition shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(245,158,11,0.3)] hover:scale-105">
                        Lancer mon projet
                    </a>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400 font-medium">
                        <div class="flex -space-x-2">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-700 border-2 border-[#0B1120]"></div>
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-600 border-2 border-[#0B1120]"></div>
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-500 border-2 border-[#0B1120]"></div>
                        </div>
                        <p>Déjà +50 propriétaires <br class="hidden sm:block">en attente</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="absolute bottom-8 right-8 text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest hidden md:block">
                    Gestion Immobilière 2.0
                </div>
                
                <div class="absolute bottom-8 right-8 border border-white/20 p-4 rounded-2xl hidden md:block">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"></path></svg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="fonctionnalites" class="relative z-20 -mt-20 px-4 md:px-12">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
                
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[2rem] shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition duration-300">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-orange-100 text-[#F59E0B] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6">
                        $
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#0B1120] mb-3">Paiement Mobile Money</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Encaissement automatique via Wave & Orange. Réconciliation instantanée et génération de quittance.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[2rem] shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition duration-300">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-red-100 text-red-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6">
                        ⚖️
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#0B1120] mb-3">Bouton Rouge Juridique</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Un impayé ? Activez la procédure d'urgence. Mise en demeure et huissier déclenchés en 1 clic.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[2rem] shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition duration-300">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6">
                        🛡️
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#0B1120] mb-3">Caution Sécurisée</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Calcul exact selon la loi. Gestion transparente des retenues pour travaux à la sortie.</p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="demo" class="py-24 px-4 md:px-12 mt-10">
            <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
                
                <div class="relative">
                    <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-amber-300 rounded-[2.5rem] rotate-2 opacity-20 blur-lg"></div>
                    <div class="relative bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-12 shadow-2xl">
                        <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-10">
                            <div>
                                <p class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Mon Tableau de Bord</p>
                                <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-[#0B1120]">Vue Propriétaire</h3>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-green-100 text-green-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold">Actif</div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="space-y-4">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100">
                                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 font-bold">K</div>
                                <div class="flex-1">
                                    <p class="text-sm font-bold text-[#0B1120]">Koffi Jean</p>
                                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Villa Cocody • Loyer à jour</p>
                                </div>
                                <span class="text-green-600 font-bold text-sm">+ 250.000 F</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-red-50 rounded-2xl border border-red-100">
                                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center text-red-600 font-bold">⚠️</div>
                                <div class="flex-1">
                                    <p class="text-sm font-bold text-[#0B1120]">Alerte Impayé</p>
                                    <p class="text-xs text-red-500">Mise en demeure générée</p>
                                </div>
                                <button class="text-xs bg-red-600 text-white px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg font-bold">Voir</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <span class="text-[#F59E0B] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs mb-2 block">Simple & Efficace</span>
                    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-[#0B1120] mb-6 leading-tight">Reprenez le contrôle de vos biens.</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-slate-500 mb-10">Plus besoin de courir après les locataires ou de gérer la paperasse. ImmoFacile CI centralise tout.</p>
                    
                    <ul class="space-y-6">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs mt-1">✓</div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-[#0B1120]">Ajoutez vos biens</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Appartements, villas, studios... tout est gérable.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs mt-1">✓</div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-[#0B1120]">Invitez vos locataires</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Ils reçoivent un lien pour payer par Wave/Orange.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs mt-1">✓</div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-[#0B1120]">Dormez tranquille</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Les fonds arrivent sur votre compte, les quittances partent seules.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-20">
            <div class="bg-[#0B1120] rounded-[3rem] p-12 md:p-20 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-600 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-20 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2"></div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-orange-600 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-20 translate-x-1/2 translate-y-1/2"></div>

                <div class="relative z-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-6">Prêt à moderniser votre gestion ?</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 mb-10 text-lg">Rejoignez la communauté des propriétaires sereins d'Abidjan.</p>
                    <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
                        <a href="/signup" class="bg-[#F59E0B] hover:bg-[#d97706] text-[#0B1120] px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg transition hover:scale-105">
                            Créer mon compte gratuit
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <p class="mt-6 text-xs text-slate-500">Aucune carte bancaire requise pour commencer.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer class="mt-20 border-t border-slate-200 pt-10 pb-10">
            <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-8">
    
                <div class="text-center md:text-left">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start gap-2 mb-2">
                        <img src="/images/immo_logo.png" alt="Logo" class="h-6 w-auto grayscale opacity-70">
                        <span class="font-bold text-slate-600">ImmoFacile CI</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">&copy; 2025. Tous droits réservés.</p>
                </div>
    
                <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide">
                    <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-[#F59E0B] transition">Politique de Confidentialité</a>
                    <a href="/cgu" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-[#F59E0B] transition">CGU & Mentions Légales</a> 
                    <a href="mailto:contact@webappci.com" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-[#F59E0B] transition">Support</a>
                </div>
    
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 font-bold">Développé par</span>
                    <a href="https://webappci.com" target="_blank" class="group hover:opacity-80 transition block">
                        <img src="/images/logo_webappci.png" alt="WebApp CI" class="h-10 w-auto object-contain group-hover:scale-105 transition">
                    </a>
                </div>
    
            </div>
        </footer>

    </div>

</body>
</html>
